<L>__{interior the bedroom, with louis}
<A>__{he carries the syringes and ampoules of morphine over to the window. his hair has gone partially white. he fills all three syringes with morphine (using two ampoules for each syringe i.e., enough to kill a polar bear) and puts them in the left breast pocket of his shirt. he puts the spare ampoules in the right breast pocket of his shirt. louis is slowly going insane. what remains of his rationality is like a rapidly fraying rope.}
